        <p>
          To be able to submit your legal questions, you'll need to register
          your account and provide some information. \n You can submit as many
          inquiries as you want. See examples below:
        </p>

        <blockquote>
          <b>Category</b>: "Green Card", <b>Question</b>: "I need help
          applying."<br />
          <b>Category</b>: "TPS", <b>Question</b>: "Any update on my
          application?"<br />
          <b>Category</b>: "Family Reunification", <b>Question</b>: "I need to
          schedule an appointment."
        </blockquote>
        <div class="sdblg">
          <p>Please don't forget to logout before leaving the site.</p>
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/log-out">LOG OUT</a>
