          inquiries as you want. See examples below:
        </p>

        <p>
          <b>Category</b>: "Green Card", <b>Question</b>: "I need help
          applying."<br />
          <b>Category</b>: "TPS", <b>Question</b>: "Any update on my
          application?"<br />
          <b>Category</b>: "Family Reunification", <b>Question</b>: "I need to
          schedule an appointment."
